│ inbounds nuw i8, ptr %p, i64 4.\n- %gep2 is canonicalized to getelementptr    │
│ i8, ptr %p, i64 8 (no inbounds).\n- The foldGEPOfPhi rewrites the phi of      │
│ pointers into %1 = phi i64 [4, %if], [8, %else] and then %2 = getelementptr   │
│ inbounds nuw i8, ptr %p, i64 %1, preserving both inbounds and nuw from %gep1. │
