│ not have those flags. Inbounds and NUW/NSW are path-sensitive; applying them  │
│ to a merged operation with a PHI index is only valid if all incoming GEPs     │
│ have those flags. Failing to intersect/strip flags strengthens assumptions    │
│ and introduces poison.\n\n4. Proposed Edit Point(s):\nModify foldGEPOfPhi to  │
